random_key2: Aapko apna peechla wala program aise modify karna hai jiske vajah se, "Kuch Aur" click karne par koi random quote aur uska author aaye.
random_key4: Iske liye aapko Math.random() function use karna hoga.
random_key5: **Math.random()** se 0 se 1 ke beech mei koi random number aata hai.
random_key6: Aapko agar 0 se 4 ke beech mei random number chahiye toh Math.random() ko 4 se multiply kar do.
random_key7: Uske baad bhi kuch decimal (yaani dashamlav) ke aage kuch hoga, jisko hatane ke liye aap Math.floor function use kar sakte ho.
